1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:00,490 --> 00:00:01,490
Korn,

3
00:00:01,570 --> 00:00:03,580
wait for me.

4
00:00:04,490 --> 00:00:06,790
Can you come to have lunch with me?

5
00:00:07,990 --> 00:00:09,990
